  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, org.apache.tools.ant.types.selectors.SelectorContainer

    public class IgniteDeploymentGarAntTask
extends org.apache.tools.ant.taskdefs.Zip
    Ant task for generating GAR file. This task extends standard zip Ant task and has two parameters:
    • basedir - Base directory for GAR archive.
    • descrdir - Directory where descriptor DESC_NAME file is located. If not specified, it is assumed that Ignite descriptor will be searched in base directory (see setBasedir(File)). Note further that GAR descriptor file is fully optional itself for GAR archive.
